2008-10-24  Henri Häkkinen  <henux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* configure.ac: Compacted the AC_INIT directive space usage.
	* src/Makefile.am: Moved AM_CPPFLAGS into gtk_feed_CPPFLAGS and
	gtk_feed_CFLAGS, and included -DG_LOG_DOMAIN=\"GTK-Feed\" to
	gtk_feed_CFLAGS.
	* src/common.c: Removed the `#include <glib.h>' and included the
	individual `<glib/xxx>' headers instead.
	* src/options.[ch]: Implemented the basic command line option
	parser.
	* src/rssfeed.c: Included the missing glib includes, removed some
	unused variables and corrected some parameters.

